Gabriel Jabbour https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabriel_Jabbour 0 Gabriel Jabbour (Arabic: غبريال جبّور) (November 7, 1922 - September 20, 1987) was a French actor. He made his debut in acting in 1957 in L'affaire Sarret-Schmidt on television. Between then and 1987 he made almost 70 appearances in film and TV with his career at its peak in the 1970s. In 1981 Jabbour appeared in the thriller series Affaire Labricole, L. He retired from acting in 1987.
